<P>
   CLINTON-DEFENSE (San Francisco) _ The chance to defend President
Clinton against charges of impeachment in a Senate trial would be
the ultimate dream case to some local defense lawyers, but others
said their skills would be useless in what will amount to a
political event, not a legal one. With impeachment by the House
looming, it appears President Clinton will need a good criminal
defense lawyer. By ULYSSES TORASSA.
