A4783 &Cx1f; tad-z
r i &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-PANAMA-RIVALS-$ADV20-     12-17 0550
</HEADER>
<BODY>
<SLUG> BC-PANAMA-RIVALS-$ADV20-COX </SLUG>
<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    NEIGHBORS PROPOSE FRESH CHALLENGES TO PANAMA'S MONEY-MAKING
DITCH
 &HT;    With PANAMA-CANAL-$ADV20.
