century ago, Bill Clinton is not going to give up the power and
perquisites of the presidency without a struggle. But if the
``comeback kid'' is to save his presidency, he is going to have to
give the performance of a lifetime when the 106th Congress convenes
in January. By ROBERT E. THOMPSON.
</P>
