romantic comedy, ``You've Got Mail,'' goes out of its way to
endorse a set of latter-day institutions _ America Online,
Starbucks, super bookstores _ deemed questionable in the eyes of
many consumers.But it's highly unlikely many will find fault with
the movie's most celebrated institutions, its eminently likable
stars Tom Hanks and Meg Ryan. 3{ stars. By Glenn Whipp. 
