<P>
   INTERNATIONAL NEWS (``i'' category)
</P>
<P>
   US-PALESTINIANS (Bethlehem) _ Just two days after welcoming
President Clinton to the holy town, Palestinians in Bethlehem burn
American flags to protest the airstrikes against Iraq that Clinton
ordered after returning from a Middle East peace mission. By
DEBORAH HORAN.
</P>
