<P>
   &UR; STREET  &LR; _ The awkward confluence of war and impeachment could
easily make an already choppy stock market even more erratic, but
efforts to expel President Clinton are not expected to trigger a
market collapse or economic recession. By columnist Mark Veverka
</P>
<P>
   &UR; WORKWAYS  &LR; _ &UR;  &LR; Ilana DeBare's workplace column.
</P>
